OL,3,CScottish nurse in trans doctor
OL,4,Cchanging room row wins partial
OL,5,Charassment claim
OL,7,FAn employment tribunal has partially
OL,8,Fupheld Sandie Peggie's claim for
OL,9,Fharassment, but rejected other
OL,10,Fallegations of discrimination. ITV
OL,11,FNews Correspondent Peter Smith reports
OL,13,FA Scottish nurse who objected to
OL,14,Fsharing a female changing room with a
OL,15,Ftransgender doctor has won part of her
OL,16,Femployment tribunal against an NHS
OL,17,Ftrust.
