OL,5,Charassment claim
OL,7,FSandie Peggie was suspended from NHS
OL,8,FFife in January last year after
OL,9,Fcomplaining about having to share a
OL,10,Fchanging room with Dr Beth Upton at
OL,11,FVictoria Hospital in Kirkcaldy on
OL,12,FChristmas Eve 2023.
OL,14,FShe was placed on special leave after
OL,15,FDr Upton, a transgender medic, made an
OL,16,Fallegation of bullying and harassment,
OL,17,Fand cited concerns about patient care.
