OL,7,FMs Peggie had lodged a claim against
OL,8,Fboth Upton and NHS Fife, citing the
OL,9,FEquality Act 2010, including sexual
OL,10,Fharassment, harassment related to a
OL,11,Fprotected belief, indirect
OL,12,Fdiscrimination and victimisation.
OL,14,FThe employment tribunal hearings took
OL,15,Fplace in Dundee earlier this year and
OL,16,Fin a written ruling published on
OL,17,FMonday, the harassment claim was
OL,18,Fupheld.
