OL,7,FHowever, Ms Peggie's claims of
OL,8,Fdiscrimination, indirect
OL,9,Fdiscrimination and victimisation
OL,10,Fagainst the doctor were dismissed.
OL,12,FMs Peggie welcomed the decision from
OL,13,FJudge Sandy Kemp and said the past two
OL,14,Fyears had been "agonising".
OL,16,FMs Peggie's solicitor, Margaret
OL,17,FGribbon, described the tribunal's
OL,18,Ffinding as "a huge win for a tenacious
OL,19,Fand courageous woman standing up for
OL,20,Fher sex-based rights".
