OL,7,FThe 318-page ruling found that NHS
OL,8,FFife had harassed Ms Peggie by not
OL,9,Frevoking Dr Upton's permission to use
OL,10,Fthe women's changing room on an
OL,11,Finterim basis after her initial
OL,12,Fcomplaint until different work rotas
OL,13,Ffor the pair could take effect.
