OL,7,FIt said that, as a result, Dr Upton
OL,8,Fwas in the changing room when Ms
OL,9,FPeggie was present on two occasions.
OL,11,FThe ruling also found the board took
OL,12,Fan "unreasonable" length of time to
OL,13,Finvestigate the patient care
OL,14,Fallegations against Ms Peggie.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for NHS Fife said: "NHS
OL,17,FFife recognises that this has been a
OL,18,Fcomplex and lengthy process and
OL,19,Facknowledges the careful consideration
OL,20,Fof Judge Kemp and the tribunal panel.
