OL,7,F"The employment tribunal unanimously
OL,8,Fdismissed all of the claimant's
OL,9,Fallegations against Dr Upton and all
OL,10,Fof the allegations against the board,
OL,11,Fapart from four specific aspects of
OL,12,Fthe harassment complaint.
OL,14,F"We will now take time to work through
OL,15,Fthe detail of the judgment alongside
OL,16,Four legal team to understand fully
OL,17,Fwhat it means for the organisation.
OL,19,F"We want to recognise how difficult
OL,20,Fthis tribunal has been for everyone
OL,21,Fdirectly and indirectly involved.
